"완전한 편집 통제와 Slack 통합으로."

#: app/templates/about.html:162
msgid "Explore Briefings"
msgstr "브리핑 살펴보기"

#: app/templates/about.html:173
msgid "Publisher Embeds"
msgstr "퍼블리셔 임베드"

#: app/templates/about.html:175
