#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1200
msgid ""
"Responses include a <code>429 Too Many Requests</code> with a <code>Retry-"
"After</code> header indicating seconds until the next request is allowed."
msgstr ""
"응답에는 <code>429 Too Many Requests</code>와 다음 요청이 허용될 때까지의 초 단위를 나타내는 "
